{"tid":784071,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人明知關愛座都會照坐 甚至特登坐？","createTime":"2018-08-18T05:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T05:13:44.000Z","uid":200788,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"058a3f8fbc3da3dfc9ca5ec4348d7208a7c6993e","tid":784071,"uid":200788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:26:15.000Z","msg":"通常地鐵上面就算好多人 關愛座都係冇咩人敢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為咗改變呢個風氣 我成日都會唔理照坐（冇有需要人士嘅情況下）<br />\n啲人通常會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁望住你 但因為近年風向轉 冇人敢批鬥你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我目的唔係想攞咩彩 只係覺得讓座既然唔一定要關愛座先讓 咁你坐關愛座同普通座 根本冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有咩好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人同我一樣咁諗？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">屌你後生仔都會攰架</span></span>"},{"pid":"84b3cfdf63d387b483ea3c150d76990290efa5fd","tid":784071,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"成日都見到架車滿哂但吉左兩個關愛座 理撚得佢攰咪坐"},{"pid":"ad576154429ba02fe0433b0ceb2624548a869951","tid":784071,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83179e671b40ce64580bd7f1fc5ca0fd663299f","tid":784071,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"照坐，有人須要先讓"},{"pid":"643ee1d07071870da3185efac500419435deb429","tid":784071,"uid":54181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:09:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b78cbcbe629a1c9815bb0003c6b2b471b2c7056","tid":784071,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:11:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f7b897c068e4a2df